-s%E1%BB%B1-V%C3%A2n-L%E1%BB%97i-s%C6%A1n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Bi-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-8qUHhF_jnn--sal5StRnKg">Sùng Nghiêm sự Vân Lỗi sơn Đại Bi tự - 崇嚴事雲磊山大悲寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Thang-b%C3%A0n-ph%C3%BA/poem-zRWhSi8OLsCDGbk659PgVA">Thang bàn phú - 湯盤賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/Thi%C3%AAn-thu-gi%C3%A1m-ph%C3%BA/poem-aNFJrxFI6pAICUyX7CKLvQ">Thiên thu giám phú - 千秋鑑賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/author-EY3eHTvDpkwLbISMoUQtYg">Phạm Tông Mại</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%BAc-T%E1%BA%A1c-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-ph%E1%BB%91/poem-PbAyR9hrnDlU5BYc_nMPhg">Túc Tạc Thạch phố - 宿鑿石浦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-T%C3%B4-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Th%C3%A0nh/poem-ntePeM4NDdtMaNEF9Lu2SA">Vịnh Tô Hiến Thành - 詠蘇憲成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
